Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that Satoru?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.97,0:00:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:34.22,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ERASED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing? Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to school\Nearly again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to wolf it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, can I ask you a frank question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you meeting and what are you\Ndoing this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not doing anything bad, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving so early,\Nyou'll be hungry before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hinazuki, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've already eaten, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must be boring here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you had a TV at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Hiromi brought me\Nlots of books yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll take only another day\Nor two of being patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll see you after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:50.69,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I put in all of my son's favorite things.\N-Sachiko Fujinuma{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:53.49,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IZUMI ELEMENTARY SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The kids from Izumi Elementary\Nare coming to school!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I spent too much time in there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna give the farewell\Naddress at the graduation ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're better at public speaking, Aya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can do it, Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:17.18,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYA NAKANISHI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just have a little courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.60,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Hockey Club\N1988 National Champions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo is absent again today, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fujinuma, you haven't heard anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. She wasn't at her\Nhouse this morning either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's got a cold?\NI wonder what's up with Hinazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And the school hasn't been\Ncontacted? That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- What's wrong?\N- Normally her mom would've called.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hinazuki sure is out a lot.\N- I wish I could take off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're talking about Kayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She may show up here\Nwhen we least expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But shall we begin class?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I hate math!\N- Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.80,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STAFF ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped by her house\Nthis morning too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're relatively calm about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you always say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this,\Nyou should stay as calm as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I tried calling Kayo's house\Nyesterday and today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but no one answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I called her mother's work too,\Nbut she's absent there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Would you call the police\Nor the Child Consultation Center?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The police...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I call the police now,\Nwon't it cause someone trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I called the Child Consultation\NCenter yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like they're going today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to Kayo's house with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The root of the problem\Nis probably there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Doing your best\Nis the key to everything."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Another one of my pet expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Yashiro was already\Nmoving behind the scenes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hinazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're with the Ishikari\NDevelopment Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The lights are on,\Nso someone is probably home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we check around back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Hinazuki! Are you home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'll take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like she's been missing\Nfor three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The lights and stove are on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The recent remnants of a meal for one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo's coat is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother was here at least,\Nup until moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the mother escaped off the balcony\Nright when we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rats. I wanted to at least\Ntake the daughter into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try again tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think the mother's coming back\Nwhile we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.27,0:08:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if we leave, I'm sure she'll return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is the daughter all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We could have the police\Nlook for the mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.61,0:08:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I have a feeling Kayo is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I happen to know she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's leave for now, to make\Nthe mother think we've given up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People from the Child Consultation\NCenter went to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yashiro, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother wasn't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think this can be resolved\Ntoday or tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be separated from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing could make me happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Kayo Hinazuki was taken\Ninto protective custody,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it meant we wouldn't see her again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I think of you guys,\NI'll get a warm feeling inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, this is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this is your birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll give you your present tomorrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a promise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This moment...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels like I've waited forever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize you were so\Neasily moved, Satoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Satoru. Stay here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's gutsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:10:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened, but someone\Ncame in here late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A security guard on night duty\Nor the school janitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone lend you their\Ndirty magazines or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.52,0:10:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He kicked a box, like he was angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully it is just dirty magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was the only one who knew\Nimmediately what they were for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I finally realized\Nthat the serial killer's second victim,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:56.89,Sign Left,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AYA NAKANISHI\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:56.89,SignNC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HIROMI SUGITA\N(11 YEARS OLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:56.89,Sign Right,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KAYO HINAZUKI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aya Nakanishi, is a student\Nhere at Izumi Elementary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were still inside the loop\Nof the abduction murders.{\i0}
