Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}MARCH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between 10 and 11 pm,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kayo Hinazuki disappeared\Nfrom her home's storage shed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Footprints left around the shed\Nmatched the rubber boots{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.63,0:11:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}belonging to the Shiratori family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The culprit used a spray\Nto make her freeze to death quickly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in a cold storage room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then he returned her frozen\Nbody to the shed before dawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't stay in this bus.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's in the dead center of the murder loop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted Hina to be found,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:12:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this is kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have a pervert find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru... Do you have a plan B?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Then let's pull up stakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember this. His footprint!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's this black powder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A briquette.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me this belongs\Nto the killer too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.17,0:12:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. What good\Ndoes losing my head do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.43,0:13:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, it was a good hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A hideout a stranger enters\Nin the middle of the night is a bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now we need to get Hinazuki\Nfar from the loop of murders...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even by force.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Child Consultation Center\Nis acting too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Through our actions,\Nthe future is definitely changing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.78,0:13:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will work out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.00,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FUJINUMA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, this is your plan B?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.25,0:13:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Simple, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take one more step.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all this,\Nthe straightforward approach?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happened\Nwhen I didn't abandon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that's what you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I figured\NI'd get chewed out first...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I said that out loud.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.17,0:14:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I wouldn't scold you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did it for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed this smell\Nwhen you opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you would be home soon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and didn't know how many guests\Nwe'd have, so I made curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was I that transparent?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come in and have some curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If nobody else had come, what would\Nyou have done with all this curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, curry is good for days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean the dishes, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- See you!\N- See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Satoru Fujinuma's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru and Kayo came back to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right? That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.04,0:15:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will Kayo have to be sent\Nto an orphanage somewhere?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good question.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do have an idea about that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I couldn't see Kayo's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a favor to ask you,\NMs. Fujinuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then tomorrow at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo, you can spend the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for calling at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gaku Yashiro, a teacher\Nat Mikoto Elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling about Kayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's called Wonder Guy. Cool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One of you take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take a bath together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I wash your hair, Kayo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does it itch anywhere, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here? Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle, tickle, tickle, tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get a grip! You're 29!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch cold if you don't\Ndo a good job drying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It sounded like\Nyou were having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.78,0:17:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Those pajamas...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I bought them beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yokai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use this. The sheet's been washed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, that's sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pull that end more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like we're on a class trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me, the night view\Nfrom Mt. Hakodate is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.22,0:17:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've never been to Hakodate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I saw it in a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.36,0:18:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't use a nightlight at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Should I turn it off then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. This is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Goodnight.\N- Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I in the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said "Yeah?"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}I said it out loud.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Cut it out!\N- No chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoru, Kayo, eat it while it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What about the curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's your dinner...\Nfor the next several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's still enough left\Nfor five or six people!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should invite everyone over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:47.44,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}5th Grade, Class 4\NKayo Hinazuki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been\Nfor the last few days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You!
